setPane("sv-refined-ban-sexual-offer", createSupportMacroContent("Ban: Sexual Offer", [{"label": "Ticket", "text": "Welcome to the SUGO family!\nWe sincerely apologize for the issue you are experiencing.\n\nWelcome! We look forward to serving your needs.\n\nWe apologize for the issue you are experiencing.\n\nWe apologize for the issue you are experiencing. The reason for the ban is the posting of sexual content. You can submit an apology request to the administration between one week and ten days after the ban.\n\nWe once again sincerely apologize for the inconvenience we have caused, and we truly thank you for your patience and understanding. We wish you a happy and successful day!\n\nSUGO Customer Service Team We are always here to help.\n\nWe once again sincerely apologize for the inconvenience we have caused, and we truly thank you for your patience and understanding. We wish you a happy and successful day!\n\nSUGO Customer Service Team"}], "الحظر بسبب عروض جنسية", [{"label": "التذكرة", "text": "مرحباً بك في عائلة سوجو!\nنعتذر جداً على المشكلة التي تواجهك\n\nنعتذر عن المشكلة التي تواجهك\n\nنعتذر عن المشكلة التي تواجهك سبب الحظر العروض الجنسىه و يمكنك تقديم طلب إعتذار للأداره بعد اسبوع ل 10 ايام من وقت الحظر\n\nنكرر اعتذارنا الخالص عن الإزعاج الذي تسببنا به، ونشكركم جزيل الشكر على صبركم وسعة صدركم. نتمنى لكم يوماً سعيداً وموفقاً!\n\nفريق خدمة عملاء سوجو"}]));
